channel.title: Ruenscape Membership
channel.description:
Well, im not sure if many people know about this site so im going to introduce it... The site im talking about is http://www.gaminglagoon.com/ this site is one of those sites that you do surveys for points and then you get a prize but i know that most of these sites dont work but http://www.gaminglagoon.com/ does work... you can check youtube for gaming lagoon testimonials
the points are credited very fast and the shipment does come
the reason im introducing this is because if you get 2.7 credits which is very easy you can get an ultimate game card which is 3$ thats a runescape membership right there and if you do 2-3 surveys a month you can get free on going membership....
another cool thing is that you dont need your credit card... you do although need your address and phone number..
its hard to explain... as you can see i not very good at explaning but its easyer to go check it out
if you do want to check it out go to http://www.gaminglagoon.com/
also im not sure if you would want to refer me but if you you can sign up at http://www.gaminglagoon.com/?ref=316425 instead....
hope you guys like it ^^
